        <abstract>
            <p>GR’s letter is a gold-mine.</p>
            <p>Pleased to have Pierre Gratiolet’s comment on the embryology of greatly modified organs</p>
            <p>and GR’s valuable cases of analogous variation.</p> 
<p>Doubts craniologists, but recounts his father’s opinion that the shape of CD’s head was altered when he returned from the <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
